div.div:
NOTES:
10 wraps on ammeter sense loop increases resolution to 0.1A
Build setup and BOM changes for MaxPCB4:
* Omit RJ12 jack, solder ST4 wires to board
* Connect paddle analog rate ctl to Teensy A8 (solder to pad 8 of DB15)
* Use terminal blocks in place of stepper/servo RJ-45s
* Use levelStick drivers for RA and dec servos. Populate their 5V regs.
* Omit 2.5mm power connector, solder power wires to board
* Omit 3mm TRS connector, hardwire AUX7/8 if desired
* Omit 12VDC regulator, jumper input to output pads
* Omit Molex switch header, bridge the pads
Setup WeMos Mini D1 Pro:
*. Shift 0 Ohm link to select external antenna
Setup Adafruit Ultimate GPS module
* Solder 6-pos XH connector pin header to module
* Populate the coin cell holder with CR1220 battery
* Attach external antenna
Setup Teensy 4.1 module:
* Perform (marked) trace cut to separate VIN from VUSB
* Enables programming without removal from board
